# Firebase Realtime Database (for automatic sync)
# To set up:
# 1. Go to https://console.firebase.google.com
# 2. Create a new project
# 3. Enable "Realtime Database" (start in test mode or configure rules)
# 4. Enable "Authentication" > "Anonymous" sign-in method
# 5. Go to Project Settings > General > Your apps > Web app
# 6. Copy the configuration values below
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
VITE_FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL=
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
